            <title><![CDATA[下午察：中国年轻人为何要当“旅游特种兵”？]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[<div class="figure-media"><img class="img-fluid lazyload" data-src="https://static.zaobao.com/s3fs-public/styles/article_large_full/public/articles/2023/04/13/file7pmlh94zxpk49l0jp1z_3.jpg?VersionId=7f2hh0hUO4oUwe.5BKksF1oVm3ceNVFK&amp;itok=1Ew1gMaS" title="刚过去的清明假期，中国旅游业出现复苏迹象。图为4月4日，旅客在福州火车站准备乘车。（中新社）" alt="刚过去的清明假期，中国旅游业出现复苏迹象。图为4月4日，旅客在福州火车站准备乘车。（中新社）" src="https://static.zaobao.com/s3fs-public/styles/article_large_full/public/articles/2023/04/13/file7pmlh94zxpk49l0jp1z_3.jpg?VersionId=7f2hh0hUO4oUwe.5BKksF1oVm3ceNVFK&amp;itok=1Ew1gMaS" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></div>
